                   <div class=\"row\">","                            <div class=\"col-sm-6  \">","                                <hr>","                            </div>","                        </div>","                        <p class=\" \">","                             Are you an Enterprise with a growing number of Datapower Appliances? With security being at the forefront of all Global Organizations, it has become a... | <a class=\"linkText heavy\" href=\"../resource/get-resource.php?refId=30&amp;objectId=4&amp;eventId=10\">Read More</a>","                        </p>","                        <p class=\"greyText  \">","                           July 14 , 2015                        </p>","                                        ","                                    </div></li>","  <li><img src=\"../images/170_200/hill_road.jpg\" /></li>","  <li><img src=\"../images/170_200/me_trees.jpg\" /></li>","  <li><img src=\"../images/170_200/hill_trees.jpg\" /></li>","  <li><img src=\"../images/170_200/mountain.jpg\" /></li>","  <li><img src=\"../images/170_200/houses.jpg\" /></li>","</ul>","    </div><!--/.row-->","   </div><!--/.item-->","  </div>","    </div>","   </div>","   </div><!--/.row-->","        ","   ","    </div>","      <br/> ","            </div>"],"id":12},{"start":{"row":169,"column":2},"end":{"row":303,"column":18},"action":"insert","lines":["<div class=\"row\">","               <div class=\"col-sm-1\"></div>","                <div class=\"col-sm-6 text-left\">","                    <h1>","                 <span itemprop=\"name\" ><strong> Automated Scripting and Data Load Functions   </strong> <br>for Global Carpet Retailer</span>","                    </h1>","                </div>","                ","                <div class=\"col-sm-4 text-right\">","                    <ul class=\"breadcrumb pull-right\">","                        <li>","                            <a href=\"../\">Home</a>","                        </li>","                        <li>","                            <a href=\"success.php\">Success Stories</a>","                        </li>","                        <li class=\"active\">Commerce Case Study","                        </li>","                    </ul>","                </div>","               <div class=\"col-sm-1\"></div> ","            </div>","            <div class=\"row\">","                <div class=\"col-sm-1\"></div>","                <div class=\"col-sm-10\">","                    <hr>","                    <h5 class=\"heavy noMargin\">Customer Background","                    </h5>","                    <div class=\"row\">","                        <div class=\"col-sm-3\">","                            <hr>","                        </div><!-- This is the divider line between the heading and the content -->","                    </div>","                    <span itemprop=\"articleBody\">","                    <p class=\"methodText\">","                       Our customer is a leading distributor of building products throughout North America with an employee base of almost 1800 people. Their catalog has more than 10,000 products from over 750 suppliers which results in them servicing approximately 11,000 customers nationwide including dealers, industrial manufacturers, manufactured housing producers and home improvement retailers through their 49 distribution centers.</p> </span>","                     <h5 class=\"heavy noMargin\">Tools & Technology Environment</h5>","                      <div class=\"row\">","                        <div class=\"col-sm-3\">","                            <hr>","                        </div><!-- This is the divider line between the heading and the content -->","                    </div>","                     <p class=\"methodText\">","                        The technologies, which were used by our team and the customer for this implementation, were</p>","                    <ul>","","                        <li>Websphere Commerce Server 7.0</li>","                        <li>Websphere Application Server 7.0</li>","                        <li>IIBM Websphere Enterprise Server</li>","                        <li>JDE E1</li>","                        <li>DB2</li>","                        <li>SOLR</li>","                        <li>Adobe Scene 7</li>","                        <li>Limelight CMS</li>","                        <li>Data Power</li>","                        <li>Cast Iron</li>","                    </ul>","                    </p>","                </div>     ","               <div class=\"col-sm-1\"></div>","            </div>","            <div class=\"row\">","                <div class=\"col-sm-1\"></div>","                <div class=\"col-sm-10\">","            <h5 class=\"heavy noMargin\">The Business Challenge</h5>     ","           <div class=\"row\">","                        <div class=\"col-sm-3\">","                            <hr>","                        </div><!-- This is the divider line between the heading and the content -->","                    </div>","           <p class=\"methodText\">","               Our customer operates their business across Americas, APAC and EMEA and each region has its own master catalog with respective products. They wanted to have their product data to be maintained in a single global website in their Global Project.</p>","           <p class=\"methodText\">As part of their project they wanted the following activities to be addressed,</p>","               <ul>","                   <li>24/7 Support Services</li>","                   <li>Automation of scripts for daily delta load data report</li>","                   <li>Production releases</li>","                   <li>Build and Deployments On-Demand</li>","                   <li>Support the existing infrastructure for Americas and set up new infrastructure for new regions</li>","               </ul>","               ","             </div>","               <div class=\"col-sm-1\"></div>","               </div>","           <div class=\"row\">","               <div class=\"col-sm-1\"></div>","               <div class=\"col-sm-10\">","                 <h5 class=\"heavy noMargin\">","                    Our Solution and Services","                 </h5>","                 <div class=\"row\">","                        <div class=\"col-sm-3\">","                            <hr>","                        </div><!-- This is the divider line between the heading and the content -->","                    </div>","                 <p class=\"methodText\">","                    Our teams helped our customer to implement their Global Project for their website product catalogs through the following,               </p>","                   <ul>","                       <li>Established a team for 24/7 support and enhancements</li>","                       <li>Implemented the Automated script for daily delta data report</li>","                       <li>Monitoring all environments on continuous basis</li>","                       <li>Configured the GPDM environment from scratch</li>","                       <li>Implemented the new scripts in GPDM environment for FTP download files,staging process, delta data reports and PIM process </li>","                       <li>Actively participated in the Production releases and successfully made the environment up and running</li>","                       <li>Implemented the Scripts for APP Support team for notification and alerts on data load failure</li>","                       <li>Implemented the log archiving Scripts for all WESB environments</li>","                       <li>Daily Monitoring the RTE Adapter and also Implemented the RTE adapter Stop and start scripts</li>","                   </ul>","            </div>","            </div>","                  <div class=\"row\">","               <div class=\"col-sm-1\"></div>","               <div class=\"col-sm-10\">","                 <h5 class=\"heavy noMargin\">","                   Customer Benefits","                 </h5>","                 <div class=\"row\">","                        <div class=\"col-sm-3\">","                            <hr>","                        </div><!-- This is the divider line between the heading and the content -->","                    </div>","                 <p class=\"methodText\"> Through our services our customer achieved a number of benefits including,</p>","                     ","        <ul>","                 <li>Able to reduce the cost of man-hours significantly by automating data-load activities</li>","                 <li>Configuring scripts for sending emails on data-load failure, reducing the manual addressing cost</li>","                 <li>Successfully deployed the updated code to different environments</li>","                 ","        </ul>","                  <br>","              <a href=\"#\"><button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-md\" type=\"button\">Download Case Study</button></a><br><br><br>","             </div>","               <div class=\"col-sm-1\"></div>","           </div>","            </div>"]}],[{"start":{"row":323,"column":25},"end":{"row":323,"column":93},"action":"remove","lines":["Easy SAP Integration into your Enterprise using IBM Integration Bus "],"id":13},{"start":{"row":323,"column":25},"end":{"row":323,"column":96},"action":"insert","lines":[" Automated Scripting and Data Load Functions for Global Carpet Retailer"]}],[{"start":{"row":337,"column":28},"end":{"row":338,"column":0},"action":"insert","lines":["",""],"id":14},{"start":{"row":338,"column":0},"end":{"row":338,"column":23},"action":"insert","lines":["                       "]}],[{"start":{"row":338,"column":23},"end":{"row":339,"column":25},"action":"insert","lines":[" <h5 class=\"heavy noMarginTop\">Case Study","                    </h5>"],"id":15}],[{"start":{"row":339,"column":25},"end":{"row":340,"column":0},"action":"insert","lines":["",""],"id":16},{"start":{"row":340,"colum